properties.areaDesc: White Mountains of Graham and Greenlee Counties including Hannagan Meadow; Galiuro and Pinaleno Mountains including Mount Graham; Upper Gila River and Aravaipa Valleys including Clifton/Safford
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 3 at 3:23AM MST until February 3 at 7:00PM MST by NWS Tucson AZ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest to west winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts mainly
to 50 mph expected in the valleys. Expect higher speeds in the
mountains.

* WHERE...Upper Gila River Valley, White Mountains of Graham and
Greenlee Counties and Galiuro and Pinaleno Mountains.

* WHEN...From 10 AM to 7 PM MST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM THIS MORNING TO 7 PM MST THIS EVENING
